      "value": "<p>Your focus on defense leaves no opening for your opponents as you fire on them.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Base attack bonus +4</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you are wielding a small arm and a one-handed melee weapon or shield, firing your small arm does not provoke @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.GtSmojwt4d6rdEkm#attack-of-opportunity]{attacks of opportunity}. If you make an attack with the melee weapon used to qualify for this benefit, you lose this benefit until the end of your next turn.</p>"
